('Spicy Beef Stir Fry', 'Packed with iron and protein for heavy lifting days.', '250g Lean Beef\nBell Peppers\nOnions\nSoy Sauce', '1. Slice beef thinly.\n2. Stir fry veggies.\n3. Add beef and sauce.', 700, 60.0, 40.0, 20.0, 'img/recipes/sample3.jpg', 1, 'approved'),

