('Tuna Salad Sandwich', 'High protein easy lunch.', '1 can Tuna\nLight Mayo\nCelery\nWhole Wheat Bread', '1. Mix tuna and mayo.\n2. Spread on bread.', 450, 35.0, 40.0, 12.0, 'img/recipes/sample7.jpg', 1, 'approved'),

